<dl>
	<dt><code>inputPathToUrl("{{ inputPath }}")</code></dt>
	<dd>{{ inputPath | inputPathToUrl }}</dd>
</dl>

<p>
	Edit <code>unsupportedDemo.inputPath</code> in front matter to re-run
	the lookup. The browser port resolves against the build-time page map;
	misses (file not in last build, or <code>liquid.pageMap: false</code>)
	warn once at the console and pass through unchanged.
</p>
